，仅次于乌克兰。 </p><figure id="attachment_3804093" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3804093" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3804093" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sam-Ryder@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Sam Ryder 在 2023 年欧洲歌唱大赛总决赛中登台表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sam-Ryder@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sam-Ryder@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sam-Ryder@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sam-Ryder@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sam-Ryder@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sam-Ryder@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3804093" class="wp-caption-text"> Sam Ryder 在 2023 年欧洲歌唱大赛总决赛期间登台表演。图片来源：多米尼克·利平斯基/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>尽管因加沙战争期间<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eurovision-bosses-double-down-to-defend-decision-not-to-boycott-israel-over-gaza-war-3754132#:~:text=over%20Gaza%20war-,Eurovision%20bosses%20double%20down%20to%20defend%20decision,boycott%20Israel%20over%20Gaza%20war&amp;text=Eurovision%20organisers%20have%20defended%20their,over%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.&amp;text=It%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the,this%20Saturday%20(May%2011).">以色列参加</a>今年的赛事而遭到抗议，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/despite-protests-eurovision-2024-breaks-global-viewing-figures-3759333">2024 年欧洲电视网的全球收视率仍打破了纪录</a>。根据<a href="https://www.ebu.ch/news/2024/05/eurovision-song-contest-2024-breaks-new-records-as-hundreds-of-millions-watch-and-listen-on-tv-and-digital-platforms">EBU 的数据</a>，共有 1.63 亿观众收看了包括总决赛在内的三场现场直播赛事。</p><p>以色列的加入引发了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hundreds-of-queer-artists-urge-olly-alexander-to-boycott-eurovision-2024-over-israels-participation-3610773">LGBT+ 群体对英国代表 Olly Alexander 的抵制呼吁，</a>超过 1,000 名瑞典艺术家也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robyn-fever-ray-first-aid-kit-among-1000-swedish-artists-calling-for-eurovision-to-ban-israel-3579906">呼吁禁止以色列</a>，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robyn">Robyn</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fever-ray">Fever Ray</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/first-aid-kit">First Aid Kit</a>等。超过<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/finnish-artists-sign-petition-calling-for-israel-to-be-banned-from-eurovision-3569080">1,400 名芬兰音乐界专业人士签署了一份请愿书，禁止该国参加这项比赛</a>。</p><p>以色列最终被允许参加比赛，并且由于政治中立条款，EBU 宣布他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eurovision-have-banned-palestinian-flags-and-symbols-3753455">保留移除巴勒斯坦旗帜和标志的权利</a>。他们后来继续<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/deleted-tiktok-reveals-moment-bambie-thug-was-forced-to-remove-pro-palestinian-message-its-fucked-up-3755454">审查爱尔兰选手 Bambie Thug，因为她在服装上隐藏了“停火”和“巴勒斯坦自由”字样</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olly-alexander">Olly Alexander</a>在比赛中演唱了歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olly-alexander-shares-new-solo-single-and-eurovision-entry-dizzy-3595340">“Dizzy”</a> ，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olly-alexander-truly-grateful-for-eurovision-support-calls-getting-zero-points-iconic-3756355">在 25 个国家/地区中获得第 18 名</a>。陪审团只给他打了 46 分，但公众投票却没有给他打分。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eurovision-2025-stage-look-and-ticket-info-revealed-3823051">2025 年欧洲歌唱大赛后：舞台、外观和门票信息</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发布。</p> ;
